    %% CRD Relationships
    PipelineCR -->|watched by| APIServer
    PipelineVersionCR -->|validated/mutated by| WebhookServer
    ScheduledWFCR -->|managed by| ScheduledWF
    ViewerCR -->|managed by| ViewerController
    WorkflowCR -->|watched by| PersistenceAgent

    %% Internal flows
    APIServer -->|creates| WorkflowCR
    ScheduledWF -->|creates| WorkflowCR
    PersistenceAgent -->|reports status to| APIServer
    UI -->|API calls| APIServer
    UI -->|fetches artifacts| MinIO
    Driver -->|resolves inputs via| APIServer
    Driver -->|logs metadata to| MLMD
    Launcher -->|uploads artifacts to| MinIO
    Envoy -->|proxies to| MLMD

    %% External dependency flows
    APIServer -->|CRD operations| K8sAPI
    APIServer -->|stores metadata| MySQL
    APIServer -->|stores artifacts| MinIO
    CacheServer -->|checks cache| MySQL
    DSPOperator -->|deploys & manages| DSP

